msgid "maxframe.dataframe.Index.droplevel"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.droplevel.index_droplevel:1 of
msgid "Return index with requested level(s) removed."
msgstr "返回删除了指定层级的索引。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.droplevel.index_droplevel:3 of
msgid ""
"If resulting index has only 1 level left, the result will be of Index "
"type, not MultiIndex. The original index is not modified inplace."
msgstr ""
"如果结果索引只剩一个层级，则结果将为 Index 类型，而不是 MultiIndex。原"
"索引不会被就地修改。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.droplevel.index_droplevel of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.indexing.droplevel.index_droplevel:6 of
msgid ""
"If a string is given, must be the name of a level If list-like, elements "
"must be names or indexes of levels."
msgstr ""
"如果给定的是字符串，必须是某个层级的名称；如果是类列表，则元素必须是层级"
"的名称或索引。"

